Bootstrap: localimage
From: ./ubuntu_22.04.sif

%labels
    Author      ChatGPT
    Description Environment for the disk-write dd benchmark task

%post
    set -e

    # Update package lists and install required tools
    apt-get update
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
        python3 \
        python3-pip \
        coreutils  # guarantees `dd` is present

    # Install pytest for the assessment framework
    pip3 install --no-cache-dir pytest

    # Create the expected home directory; leave benchmark dir absent
    mkdir -p /home/user
    chmod 0777 /home/user   # ensure the learner (non-root) can write here

    # Clean up apt cache to keep the image lean
    apt-get clean
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

%runscript
    chmod 755 /home/user

    # Default runscript: just execute given command inside the container
    exec "$@"

%help
    This Apptainer image provides a minimal Ubuntu 22.04 environment with
    Python, pytest, and coreutils (for `dd`) pre-installed.
    The directory /home/user is writable so that learners can complete the
    disk-write benchmark exercise.